OL,4,C'inadequate' - watchdog sends warning
OL,5,Cto NHS
OL,7,FMaternity services in Taunton and
OL,8,FYeovil have been declared "inadequate"
OL,9,Fby the health watchdog.
OL,11,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,12,Fdiscovered a string of issues across
OL,13,Fmultiple hospitals when they inspected
OL,14,FSomerset NHS Foundation Trust's
OL,15,Fmaternity services in November.
OL,26,@pD@[OUpD@fO]
