OL,4,C'inadequate' - watchdog sends warning
OL,5,Cto NHS
OL,7,FThe reports have now been published
OL,8,Fand a warning notice sent to bosses at
OL,9,FMusgrove Park and Yeovil District
OL,10,Fhospitals. Bridgwater Community
OL,11,FHospital's maternity services was also
OL,12,Finspected and require improvement.
OL,14,FIn Taunton, inspectors found there was
OL,15,Fnot enough equipment to resuscitate
OL,16,Fbabies in an emergency. There was also
OL,17,Fnot always enough midwifery staff to
OL,18,Fkeep people safe.
