OL,7,FStaff also failed to complete
OL,8,Fmandatory training - with gaps
OL,9,Fincluding how to protect people from
OL,10,Fabuse and how to manage when unborn
OL,11,Fbabies had reduced movements or growth
OL,12,Frestrictions.
OL,14,FA lack of emergency equipment was also
OL,15,Fan issue in Yeovil and inspectors also
OL,16,Ffound the service did not always
OL,17,Fcontrol infection well - saying staff
OL,18,Fdid not always clean their hands.
