OL,7,FIn Bridgwater, the CQC highlighted
OL,8,Fissues around leadership, wait times
OL,9,Fand how equipment was maintained. It
OL,10,Falso found lessons were not always
OL,11,Flearned following incidents.
OL,13,FHigh sickness levels among staff in
OL,14,FBridgwater also saw some services
OL,15,Fclosed for five months of the year.
