OL,7,FCarolyn Jenkinson, CQC's deputy
OL,8,Fdirector of secondary and specialist
OL,9,Fcare said inspectors found a
OL,10,F"deterioration" in the quality of care
OL,11,Fbeing provided across the Trust's
OL,12,Fmaternity services.
OL,14,F"We also had particularly significant
OL,15,Fconcerns with the care being provided
OL,16,Fat Musgrove Park Hospital and Yeovil
OL,17,FDistrict Hospital," she added.
