OL,7,F"Leaders weren't supporting staff to
OL,8,Flearn from incidents or make
OL,9,Fimprovements when things went wrong.
OL,10,FIncident data seen by inspectors also
OL,11,Fdidn't always match up with
OL,12,Finformation provided to the trust's
OL,13,Fboard.
OL,15,F"Leaders also weren't effectively
OL,16,Fmonitoring how the services performed,
OL,17,For taking action when risks needed to
OL,18,Fbe escalated."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
