OL,7,FShe also highlighted "poor systems"
OL,8,Ffor assessing women who need medical
OL,9,Fattention at Musgrove Park.
OL,11,FSpeaking about Yeovil, she added: "We
OL,12,Fwere concerned that staff weren't
OL,13,Falways cleaning their hands when
OL,14,Fentering clinical areas to care for
OL,15,Fpeople, and they weren't always
OL,16,Ffollowing the trust's uniform policy
OL,17,Fto help reduce spreading germs.
OL,18,FLeaders also weren't monitoring
OL,19,Fwhether staff were complying with
OL,20,Ftheir hand hygiene policies."
