OL,7,FMs Jenkinson highlighted high rates of
OL,8,Fstaff sickness at Bridgwater, saying
OL,9,Fpoor staffing levels meant the birth
OL,10,Fcentre and home birth service had to
OL,11,Fclose for five months between February
OL,12,Fand July.
OL,14,F"However, the trust had taken steps to
OL,15,Frecruit more midwives," she said.
OL,16,F"They should also review how to ensure
OL,17,Fthe service is sustainable for local
OL,18,Fwomen and people."
