OL,7,FIn a statement, Chief Executive of
OL,8,FSomerset NHS Foundation Trust Peter
OL,9,FLewis said the Trust has made
OL,10,Fsignificant changes since the
OL,11,Finspection.
OL,13,F"We want to say sorry to our families
OL,14,Fthat use these services and to our
OL,15,Fhard-working colleagues," he said.
