OL,7,F"We are committed to improve, so that
OL,8,Fwe provide an excellent service that
OL,9,Fsupports women, birthing people, and
OL,10,Ffamilies in Somerset. We have made
OL,11,Fsignificant changes since the
OL,12,Finspection and will continue to do so."
OL,14,FHe added: "We are here to support all
OL,15,Fthose using our maternity services. If
OL,16,Fyou have any questions, or concerns,
OL,17,Fwould like more information, or to
OL,18,Fspeak to someone about our service,
OL,19,Fplease speak to your midwife. We are
OL,20,Fhere to help and support you."
